HC10T6
Mutual Recursion in Eq for Blockchain
Modify the Eq type class to use mutual recursion between == and /= in an instance for the Blockchain type.

Main.hs
data Blockchain = Blockchain Int deriving Show
instance Eq Blockchain where
    x == y = not (x /= y)
    Blockchain a /= Blockchain b = a /= b
main :: IO ()
main = do
    print (Blockchain 5 == Blockchain 5)
    print (Blockchain 3 /= Blockchain 7)

